p= `Hello ${buyer.cooperative.lastName || ','} a member of your cooperative on ${process.env.APP_NAME} just made a purchase below are the order details`
p Customer Name <strong>#{buyer.firstName} #{buyer.lastName}</strong>
p Order Number <strong>##{order._id}</strong></p>
h3 Order Details
table(border=1)
    tr
        th Order Number
        td #{order._id}
    tr
        th Total Quantities
        td #{order.quantity}
    tr
        th Product Details
        td
            table(border=0)
                thead
                tr
                    th Product Name
                    th Quantity
                    th Unit Price
                    th Unit Subtotal
                tbody
                    tr
                        td #{order.product.name}
                        td #{order.quantity}
                        td #{order.installmentTotalRepayment/order.quantity}
                        td #{order.installmentTotalRepayment}

    tr
        th Subtotal
        td #{order.installmentTotalRepayment}

h4 Take Action
p Your action is needed for this order APPROVE : <a href="#{process.env.WEB_URL}/order/update-approval-status/#{order.approvalRecord.corporateAdminApprovalToken}/#{cooperative._id}/approved"> #{process.env.WEB_URL}/order/update-approval-status/#{order.token}/#{cooperative._id}/approved</a><br/>
<strong>Or</strong>
p DECLINE: <a href="#{process.env.WEB_URL}/order/update-approval-status/#{order.token}/#{cooperative._id}/declined"> #{process.env.WEB_URL}/order/update-approval-status/#{order.token}/#{cooperative._id}/declined</a>
